=head1 Procedure

  Part A: Link-local Address
   1. TN1 transmits Packet A an Echo Request with TN1's link-local source address.
   2. Observe the packets transmitted by the NUT.

=head1 Observable Results

  Part A
   Step 2:
   The NUT should send a Neighbor Solicitation with Target Address equal to TN1's
   link-local address, indicating that the NUT has successfully determined that TN1 was on-link.


